\ asin, acos, atan — polymorphic over floats and matrices.

\ ---- asin ----
0 asin .             \ 0
1 asin .             \ 1.5708   (pi/2)
-1 asin .            \ -1.5708

\ ---- acos ----
1 acos .             \ 0
0 acos .             \ 1.5708   (pi/2)
-1 acos .            \ 3.14159  (pi)

\ ---- atan ----
0 atan .             \ 0
1 atan .             \ 0.785398 (pi/4)
-1 atan .            \ -0.785398

\ ---- round trip ----
1 atan tan .         \ 1

\ ---- polymorphic over a matrix ----
[ 0 1 ] 1 2 matrix atan .       \ [0 0.785398]

\ ---- failure ----
"x" asin
